{"tid":2065051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前員工爆料被刪po：華為7月將裁員50%近十萬人","createTime":"2020-06-15T09:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T13:03:20.000Z","uid":125168,"like":294,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"50cfb5eb1f609b885d0d9e4031b5067c108916e1","tid":2065051,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"美國將加重對華為制裁，擬升級出口管制，恐對華為造成衝擊。消息傳出，華為可能將於7月中旬宣布大變革，其中涉及股權和裁員約50%，從19萬降至10萬人。<br />\n<br />\n6月14日，新浪微博認證為「華為前員工李洪元」的微博帳號leedeson貼出一張群組討論的截圖顯示，華為可能將於7月中旬宣布大變革，其中涉及股權和裁員，從19萬降至10萬人，並提到很多退休的都選擇一半股票兌現另一半保留。<br />\n<br />\n目前該微博已刪貼。李洪元曾在華為工作12年，去年爆出要求離職補償，卻遭公司反告敲詐勒索，在公安局羈押251天後，無罪釋放，並獲大陸國家賠償人民幣10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/4636722?utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_source=udnnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F4636722%3Futm_medium%3Dfb%26utm_source%3Dudnnews&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7v5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=a22ddce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/4636722?utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_source=udnnews</a>"},{"pid":"8123c461be9e8ea703ae4513324e4bb28423ba51","tid":2065051,"uid":187489,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[PP見] A4紙5秒自製白絲帶，唔好再俾藉口自己！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2064961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2064961</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n6點前入去like同推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打 最後召集 黑衫已太遲<br />\n轉pin呢個丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171b3b7b123a190b5470e56503f9bc7f4f251958","tid":2065051,"uid":19287,"like":56,"dislike":6,"score":50,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"卻遭公司反告敲詐勒索，在公安局羈押251天後，無罪釋放，並獲大陸國家賠償人民幣10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<b